title: Tim Dillon
itunes:title: Tim Dillon
description:
My HoneyDew this week is Tim Dillon! Tim returns to talk more about his parents - his mom is a former mermaid who currently suffers from schizophrenia and his dad is a former musician who is currently still a former musician. Tim shares stories about hanging out in crack houses, doing cocaine and drinking in middle school. He also talks about coming out of the closet and what it was like when his subprime mortgage gig bottomed out. It’s a wild one!
